  "texts": [
    "This verification status is used by researchers in detecting a user\"s reliability [53].",
    "When using user-based features, it is important to understand that the availability of this information is a critical concern due to privacy and access constraints on some platforms such as Twitter.2) Post-based features: Post-based features can be used to identify the veracity of news from different aspects relevant to social media posts [12].",
    "This includes analyses of user feedback, reactions, opinions, and responses, in general, as indicators of fake news.",
    "Some of these features include comments, likes, tagging, user ratings, sentiment, and emotional reactions [42].",
    "Some research dealing with postbased features have dealt with a number of retweets, likes, shares, and others [54][55]."
  ]
}